53:22.366 --> 53:24.201
Never mind, it's a compliment.

53:24.326 --> 53:25.619
Oh. Thank you.

53:25.703 --> 53:28.205
I'll give you one,
just as soon as I can make one up.

53:28.580 --> 53:31.709
Can't you think of a compliment
without making it up?

53:32.584 --> 53:33.752
Well...

53:36.046 --> 53:37.214
Try.

53:38.882 --> 53:40.426
Try real hard.

53:40.551 --> 53:42.052
