53:42.386 --> 53:43.887
MAN: Hey, Toby,

53:45.014 --> 53:47.266
how are the fish running today?

53:47.391 --> 53:49.935
You ain't got your mind on work,
though, have you?

53:50.060 --> 53:51.228
