53:51.353 --> 53:54.773
This is about as private as a subway.
Come with me.

53:54.898 --> 53:56.358
I ain't got any secrets.

53:56.442 --> 53:59.987
Well, we just can't have
a good interview with people intruding.

54:00.070 --> 54:01.113
Oh.

