55:50.681 --> 55:53.684
Nobody yells "help."
They always yell "help, help."

55:53.809 --> 55:55.436
So I was waiting for the other "help,"

55:55.519 --> 55:58.522
and when you didn't say "help,"
well, I said "help."

55:59.022 --> 56:00.315
I see.

56:00.524 --> 56:03.485
This isn't going to be
quite as easy as I expected.

56:04.069 --> 56:06.029
Now, the third word.

56:07.030 --> 56:08.198
Steal.

56:08.449 --> 56:09.533
Home.

56:10.075 --> 56:14.329
Oh, you poor boy. You think
somebody's trying to steal your home.

56:14.413 --> 56:16.206
Willie Mays stole home.

56:16.832 --> 56:18.375
Who's Willie May?

56:18.500 --> 56:21.336
Not May, Mays. He's a baseball player.

56:21.420 --> 56:24.339
Oh, never mind.
The association speaks for itself.

56:25.382 --> 56:26.925
Now, number four.

56:29.094 --> 56:30.262
Girl.

56:31.555 --> 56:32.848
Dad.

56:34.099 --> 56:35.476
Holy Moses.

56:35.559 --> 56:36.685
Something wrong?

56:37.519 --> 56:40.939
Toby, I'll just have to ask you
to explain that one for me.

56:41.231 --> 56:43.358
That's the song they're playing.

56:43.775 --> 56:49.239
<i>On top of Old Smoky
Where things get real hot</i>

