Any more words?

58:43.854 --> 58:46.023
Yes. Love.

58:46.523 --> 58:47.858
Thirty.

58:48.859 --> 58:50.527
You think love begins at 30?

58:50.652 --> 58:53.363
No, ma'am.
Love is when you ain't got any.

58:54.698 --> 58:55.866
Any what?

58:55.949 --> 58:58.410
Any points. Like in tennis.

58:58.744 --> 59:02.372
Love-15, love-30, love-40.

59:03.373 --> 59:04.791
Maybe I should've said love-15,

